Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在某天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講了漫長的電話後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她在我身旁哭了很長的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想錯的並不是她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一直注視著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是比任何人都更體貼 比任何人都漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都更充實地活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽得到她的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…誰…
